# Week 7 & 8: AI-Powered Industrial Quality Assurance System

## 🎯 Project Overview
This phase marks the completion of the Multi-Modal AI QA system. We integrated our custom-trained YOLOv8 vision model with a localized LLM (Llama 3.2 via Ollama) into a unified, interactive web application built with Streamlit.

## ⚙️ Features
- **Defect Detection:** Uploads a steel surface image and draws bounding boxes around detected defect classes using the trained `best.pt` model weights.
- **AI Report Generation:** Automatically parses the vision model's confidence scores and feeds them via prompt engineering into Llama 3.2 to generate a structured industrial maintenance report.
- **Local Deployment:** Runs fully locally on the host machine to ensure private industrial data is never exposed to external cloud APIs.
